I"<h1 id="about-me">About me</h1>

<p>I’m a linguist from Denmark and a PhD candidate at the University of Newcastle in Australia. I currently research spatial language and cognition in Indigenous Australian languages. I completed my master’s degree at the University of Copenhagen in Functional and Cognitive Linguistics.</p>

<p>My research interests cover a range of related fields such as anthropological linguistics, cognitive science, and semantic typology.</p>

<p>See more about what I do under <a href="/research/">research</a></p>
